DEMOS AND COMPILED ARTIFACTS
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

The interactive demos under demos/ run WebAssembly modules
(demos/assets/wasm/*.wasm and their JavaScript loaders) that are compiled
from the Phi-Coherent C++ packages (the phi-* and phi-quantum-* source trees),
each of which is itself licensed under AGPL-3.0-only.  The corresponding
source for those modules is the source of those packages.

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
THIRD-PARTY CONTENT
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

This site has no third-party runtime dependencies.  All HTML, CSS, and
JavaScript are first-party works.  Audio clips under demos/assets/audio/ are
used solely as input samples for the codec demonstrations.
